软提供的 30 亿美元巨额分手支票放弃这笔交易。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-07-13/microsoft-activision-weigh-sale-of-some-uk-cloud-gaming-rights?sref=10lNAhZ9"><ins>有报道称，</ins></a>微软可能会在英国出售一些云游戏版权，以满足 CMA 的担忧。微软已与第三方云游戏公司签署协议，在其平台上提供其游戏，这足以让欧盟<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-eu-approves-microsofts-687-billion-activision-blizzard-takeover-160319415.html"><ins>批准合并</ins></a>。</p><p>与此同时，FTC 仍定于 8 月 2 日开始就此次收购举行自己的证据听证会。该机构<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/ftc-microsoft-activision-blizzard-antitrust-competition-lawsuit-191341476.html"><ins>提起诉讼以阻止合并</ins></a>，并寻求初步禁令，以阻止微软和动视暴雪在将案件送交审判之前完成交易，但没有成功。</p><p>因此，微软和动视肯定会急于在 8 月初之前解决此事。有人建议，尽管存在 CMA 争议，但他们仍会尝试在最初的截止日期前完成合并，并找到解决方法以继续在英国开展业务，但由于各方都愿意找到友好的解决方案，目前看来这不太可能。 <a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/uk-competition-regulator-extends-microsoft-activision-investigation-by-six-weeks-103541516.html"><ins>CMA 给自己额外的六周时间</ins></a>，即 8 月 29 日，对此案做出最终决定。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/microsoft-and-a-uk-regulator-have-been-granted-more-time-to-resolve-activision-merger-issues-191354797.html ?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/microsoft-and-a-uk-regulator-have-been-granted-more-time-to-resolve-activision-merger-issues-191354797.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> c887ebb8-dfaf-4ab6-9071-1444174d4986</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jul 2023 19:13:54 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1689621235</ingested><modified> 2023-07-17T19:14:01+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Mergers, Acquisitions & Takeovers]]></category><category><![CDATA[Business]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="4295" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/519478b0-21c6-11ee-bfcd-7409d88423e8" width="6152"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="4295" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/519478b0-21c6-11ee-bfcd-7409d88423e8" width="6152"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[NurPhoto via Getty Images]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[The Acitvision Blizzard Call of Duty game is seen in the Apple App Store in this photo illustration on 13 March, 2023 in Warsaw, Poland. (Photo by Jaap Arriens/NurPhoto via Getty Images)]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[FTC To Appeal Microsoft Activision Case]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[The best smartwatches for 2023]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>就在几年前，购买智能手表的理由还不清楚。市场并不像今天这样饱和，功能也更加有限。如今，可穿戴设备世界充满了各种高质量的选择，Apple Watch、三星 Galaxy Watch 和 Fitbit Versa 等一些关键厂商凭借其智能功能脱颖而出。如果您正在阅读本指南，您可能已经决定是时候升级手腕上的任何小工具了 - 无论是标准手表还是老化的智能手表。无论您属于哪一类，在决定购买哪一款最适合的智能手表之前，您需要考虑的规格列表很长，我们将帮助您理解它。</p><h2>在智能手表中寻找什么</h2><figure><img src="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-04/59a8ed60-7819-11ea-a2fe-460c6da1595e" alt="智能手表上的 Google WearOS 界面。" data-uuid="472f010c-5b6c-3f53-b14e-d885b4a92446"><figcaption><div class="photo-credit">彻林·洛</div></figcaption></figure><h3>兼容性</h3><p>Apple Watch 只能与 iPhone 配合使用，而 Wear OS 设备则可以与 iOS 和 Android 手机配合使用。三星、Garmin、Fitbit 等制造的智能手表也与 Android 和 iOS 兼容，但您需要在智能手机上安装配套应用程序。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>智能手表操作系统还将规定您可以访问的第三方应用程序的类型和数量。然而，其中许多因素并没有什么用处，使得这一因素在宏伟的计划中成为相当次要的因素。</p><h3>价格</h3><p>最好的智能手表价格通常在 300 至 400 美元之间。与价格在 100 至 250 美元之间的廉价智能手表相比，这些价格较高的设备具有先进的操作系统、通信、音乐和健身功能。它们通常还包括机载 GPS 跟踪、音乐存储和 NFC 等额外功能，而预算设备通常不具备这些功能。</p><p>一些公司生产专门的健身手表：这些手表的价格很容易就超过 500 美元，我们只向认真的运动员推荐它们。泰格豪雅<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag-heuer-connected-calibre-e4-golf-edition-093031897.html">（TAG Heuer）</a>和宇舶表（Hublot）等品牌的豪华智能手表也可以达到天价，但我们不会认可其中任何一个。这些设备的价格可能超过 1,000 美元，而且您通常只需要购买一个品牌名称和一些不必要的异国情调的构建材料即可。</p><h3>电池寿命</h3><p>电池寿命仍然是我们对智能手表最大的抱怨之一，但最近还是有希望的。您可以使用 Apple Watch 和大多数 Wear OS 设备享受整整两天的时间。使用 Snapdragon Wear 3100 处理器的手表支持扩展电池模式，如果您愿意关闭除显示时间之外的大多数功能，则一次充电可保证长达五天的电池续航时间。 Snapdragon 的下一代 Wear 4100 和 4100+ 处理器已于 2020 年发布，但<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/razer-x-fossil-gen-6-smartwatch-gamers-160007878.html">迄今为止只有少数设备（其中一些设备尚未上市</a>）在使用它们。其他型号可以持续五到七天，但它们通常具有较少的功能和较低质量的显示屏。与此同时，一些健身手表一次充电即可使用数周。</p><p>一些智能手表现在也支持更快的充电。例如，苹果承诺 Series 7 只需 45 分钟即可从零电量增加到 80%，并在 75 分钟内充满电。 OnePlus Watch 的速度更快，只需 10 分钟即可从 0% 充至 43%。 （请注意，这是该设备唯一的优点之一。）</p><h3>沟通</h3><p>任何值得考虑的智能手表都会向您的手腕发送电话、短信和应用程序通知。通话和短信提醒是不言自明的，但如果这些对您来说意义重大，请考虑使用支持 LTE 的手表。它们比仅支持 WiFi 的同类产品更昂贵，但蜂窝连接使智能手表可以接听电话，并且可以在设备不在附近的情况下处理短信。就应用程序警报而言，将它们发送到您的手腕上将使您可以向下看一眼表盘，看看您现在是否确实需要检查手机。</p><h3>健身追踪</h3><p>活动跟踪是人们转向智能手表的一个重要原因。通用手表应该充当健身追踪器，记录您的步数、卡路里和锻炼情况，并且当今的大多数可穿戴设备还具有心率监测器。</p><p>许多智能手表的健身功能包括内置 GPS，这对于跟踪跑步和骑自行车的距离非常有用。游泳者会想要防水的东西，值得庆幸的是，现在大多数通用设备至少可以承受在泳池中浸泡。 Garmin 等公司的一些智能手表比其他公司<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2019-07-16-the-best-gps-running-watches-for-2019.html">更注重健身</a>，并且往往提供更高级的功能，例如心率差异跟踪、恢复时间估计、板载地图等。</p><p>多年来，智能手表的健康追踪也取得了进步。 Apple 和 Fitbit 设备都可以估算血氧水平并测量心电图。但智能手表的价格越便宜，它具有这些深入的健康跟踪功能的可能性就越小。如果收集这些健康指标对您很重要，您就必须为此特权付费。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-05/2c3e5710-b8b0-11eb-ae7c-3c5baecf0395" alt="三星 Galaxy Watch Active" data-uuid="12ad0f74-e120-3940-8958-bef3c90f1d40"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">恩杰特</div></figure><h3>音乐</h3><p>您的手表不仅可以追踪您的晨跑，还可以在您锻炼时播放音乐。许多智能手表都允许您在本地保存音乐，因此您可以通过蓝牙连接无线耳机并聆听音乐，而无需携带手机。那些没有内置音乐存储空间的手表通常具有手表上的音乐控件，因此您无需拿出手机即可控制播放。如果您的手表支持 LTE，则不需要本地保存 - 您将能够直接将音乐从手表传输到配对的耳机。</p><h3>常亮显示屏</h3><p>如今，大多数旗舰智能手表都有一些常亮显示屏——有些默认开启，而另一些则允许您通过调整设置来启用它。通过这项智能功能，您无需抬起手腕即可低头看一眼手表，即可查看时间、健康状况或您设置为在表盘上显示的任何其他信息。这无疑会影响设备的电池寿命，但值得庆幸的是，大多数常亮模式都会调暗显示屏的亮度，因此它不会不必要地以峰值运行。较便宜的设备不会有此功能；相反，他们的触摸屏会自动关闭以节省电池寿命，您必须有意检查手表才能再次打开显示屏。</p><h3>近场通信</h3><p>许多智能手表都具有 NFC 功能，让您无需携带钱包即可使用非接触式支付进行支付。保存信用卡或借记卡信息后，您可以在跑步回家的路上将智能手表靠近 NFC 读卡器来支付一杯咖啡的费用。请记住，不同的手表使用不同的支付系统：Apple 手表使用 Apple Pay，Wear OS 设备使用 Google Pay，三星设备使用 Samsung Pay 等等。</p><p> Apple Pay 是最受欢迎的 NFC 支付系统之一，支持 72 个不同国家/地区的<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3N1cHBvcnQuYXBwbGUuY29tL2VuLXVzL0hUMjA0OTE2IiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI3ZjQzNGUxNi1hYWJlLTMxNGQtODhmMC1mYWM3ZDNmMjZkNTEifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAT0rwaJ5r70d13bEq45AmZjeHIkXLUYaxQAHdothfWjt&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.apple.com%2Fen-us%2FHT204916">多家银行和信用卡</a>，而三星和 Google Pay 的支持区域较少。还需要注意的是，三星和谷歌系统对 NFC 支付的支持也因设备而异。</p><h2>整体最佳：Apple Watch </h2><p><core-commerce id="9ff46d1833b9419cb35d3e076f18b898" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>自 2015 年首次亮相以来，Apple Watch 已发展成为市场上最好的可穿戴设备之一。它是 iPhone 用户最好的智能手表，我们不会因为你只是为了能够使用 Apple Watch 而改用 iPhone 来评判你。最新型号<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAYX-bazWvFbQmYatuPBRrOQtXMae8GH2LTu7ifSAN24j&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB0BDHM49BJ%2F">Apple Watch Series 8</a>具有可靠的健身追踪功能，可满足初学者和专业运动员的需求。它还可以检测您是否遭遇过车祸，可以进行心电图 (ECG) 测试并测量血氧水平。此外，这款 Apple 智能手表还提供 NFC、板载音乐存储和许多有用的应用程序、可定制功能以及消息响应方式。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-watch-series-8-real-world-test-130031046.html">Series 8</a>和之前的 Series 7 之间没有太多差异。 Watch 的设计基本没有变化，虽然 Series 8 运行在较新的 S8 SiP 上，但在我们的测试中并没有感觉速度明显加快。它的续航时间稍长一些，新的低功耗模式给我们留下了深刻的印象，该模式在电池电量已降至 20% 的情况下，还能让手表继续运行两个小时。</p><p>对于大多数人来说，Series 8 是最好的 Apple Watch，但现在还有两种相反的选择。新款<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAQBT5-cTP044Dyy6WeZt7bC3sRshEueEfwVKg4q1KI4e&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB0BDJK4G9C%2F&amp;uuid=tBCD9FeYri1sDemh11140">Apple Watch Ultra</a>对于大多数人来说可能有点大材小用，但它具有大量额外功能，例如用于跟踪潜水的额外防水功能、更准确的 GPS 以及迄今为止 Apple Watch 中最大的电池。苹果为我们当中最坚固的人设计了它，但对于普通人来说，它可能拥有比他们需要的更多的功能。</p><p>另一方面，售价 250 美元的<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9ncC9wcm9kdWN0L0IwQkRIVFFEUlo_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMnktMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjdmNDM0ZTE2LWFhYmUtMzE0ZC04OGYwLWZhYzdkM2YyNmQ1MSJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAQqfc4IgKPjlNvVsKO4isqGtt2yMpzPuyiayTUCb5oms&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB0BDHTQDRZ">Apple Watch SE</a>功能不如 Series 8 丰富，但对于大多数人来说可能已经足够了。事实上，我们认为 Watch SE 是首次购买者或预算有限的人的最佳智能手表选择。你将获得 Apple Watch 的所有核心功能，以及跌倒和碰撞检测、噪音监控和紧急求救等功能，但你将不得不使用更先进的硬件功能，例如常亮显示屏、血氧传感器、心电图监视器和皮肤温度传感器。</p> <a class="athena-button rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=shopnow-button&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAY0fiAzPqt8kgiaqHt808JPV45V3tqQgxd5IRhk-YrCd&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB0BDJK4G9C%2F" id="9694c5ea63ae49b8abf57588cc4a1111" data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;sec:shop-now;cpos:1;pos:1">在亚马逊购买 Apple Watch Ultra - 799 美元</a><a class="athena-button rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=shopnow-button&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9ncC9wcm9kdWN0L0IwQkRIVFFEUlo_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMnotMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjdmNDM0ZTE2LWFhYmUtMzE0ZC04OGYwLWZhYzdkM2YyNmQ1MSJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAWWFB8RHOFEIINRrnOxmEndozDmh7QVo1Qwk0PpR7f8K&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB0BDHTQDRZ" id="385dab946a8c44cbab484b9bbd0dc9d2" data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;sec:shop-now;cpos:1;pos:1">在亚马逊购买 Apple Watch SE - 249 美元</a><h2>最佳预算智能手表：Fitbit Versa 2 </h2><p><core-commerce id="85b3305a467442a4bb55fa552af745fe" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>花 400 美元购买智能手表并不适合每个人，这就是为什么我们推荐<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9GaXRiaXQtRml0bmVzcy1TbWFydHdhdGNoLVRyYWNraW5nLUluY2x1ZGVkL2RwL0IwN1RXRlZEV1Q_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMnktMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjdmNDM0ZTE2LWFhYmUtMzE0ZC04OGYwLWZhYzdkM2YyNmQ1MSJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAdjIwL4nz10RAZhyq20mYj-zj8OgDvtY0-Nv5KxaasDe&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FFitbit-Fitness-Smartwatch-Tracking-Included%2Fdp%2FB07TWFVDWT&amp;uuid=oDcdK5T2cT3u2dud18142">Fitbit Versa 2</a>作为 200 美元以下的最佳选择。这是我们最喜欢的经济型手表，因为它以优惠的价格提供了一系列功能。您可以获得所有这些必需品：Fitbit 可靠的运动跟踪功能（包括自动锻炼检测）、睡眠跟踪、防水、联网 GPS、血氧 (SpO2) 跟踪和六天的电池续航时间。它还支持使用 NFC 的 Fitbit Pay，并且内置 Amazon Alexa 作为语音助手。虽然 Versa 2 通常售价 150 美元，但我们看到它的价格低至 100 美元。</p><h2>最佳 Android 智能手表：三星 Galaxy Watch 5 </h2><p><core-commerce id="79b946733abc4118996172a3bb4aea66" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>三星可能没有为其广受欢迎的 Galaxy Watch 的最新版本带来太多升级，但这并不意味着<a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAWOZQlepr_6LxjFR8weEI-UI2TCVydfSxav_0PEQZVMY&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB0B2J5TB3Q%2F">Watch 5</a>仍然不是 Android 用户最好的智能手表。更耐用的触摸屏和精致的曲率等改进听起来并不令人兴奋，但它们使<a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/samsung-galaxy-watch-5-pro-review-battery-life-specs-durability-180052187.html">Watch 5</a>更具弹性和可靠。此外，Galaxy Watch 在 Wear OS 上提供最全面的健身和健康跟踪，包括身体成分分析，该公司今年还增加了睡眠指导功能，旨在帮助指导您更好地休息。</p><p>如果您不介意超大手表，请考虑<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:12;pos:1;pdid:Watch 5 Pro" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAe7cpS_IzwFlqpB2UJZ_D1tL6iZrdomTC5QMF3040r9a&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB0B2HXJZ98%2Fref%3Das_li_ss_tl" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B0B2HXJZ98/ref=as_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;linkCode=ll1&amp;tag=buyersguide2022-20&amp;language=en_US" class="rapid-with-clickid">Galaxy Watch 5 Pro</a> 。它的价格更贵，为 450 美元，但配备了更大的 45 毫米钛金属外壳、超耐用的触摸屏和更大的电池。尽管三星将这款 Android 智能手表定位为户外设备，但您最好将其视为比标准型号耐用的大型手表。它具有与 40 毫米和 44 毫米版本相同的智能手表功能，但它支持 GPX 锻炼路线格式，因此您可以在徒步旅行和骑自行车时获得逐向导航。</p><p>所有三款手表都具有防水功能，因此可以追踪游泳情况或在突如其来的暴风雨中幸存下来，并且可持续使用一天以上（无需启用“始终显示”功能）。它们还运行 Wear OS 3.5，与三星之前的 Tizen 操作系统非常相似，长期佩戴者无需担心适应新系统。最终，Galaxy Watch 5 系列是一款功能强大、功能全面的智能手表，可以很好地满足大多数 Android 用户的需求。</p><h2>时尚智能手表：Fossil 等</h2><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-01/7b17f630-523e-11eb-a357-6290b19b6ed5" alt="Michael Kors 在 CES 2021 上访问 Gen 5e MKGO" data-uuid="5e1644f4-7ccc-3889-9910-693c96aaa9d7"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">化石</div></figure><p>是的，仍然有公司试图制造“时尚”的智能手表。当可穿戴设备还很新颖且普遍丑陋时， <a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Fossil;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=b7221669-d5e1-47ff-8df7-36fe8547019c&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Fossil&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiJiNzIyMTY2OS1kNWUxLTQ3ZmYtOGRmNy0zNmZlODU0NzAxOWMiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZm9zc2lsLmNvbS9lbi11cy93YXRjaGVzL3NtYXJ0d2F0Y2hlcy8iLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjdmNDM0ZTE2LWFhYmUtMzE0ZC04OGYwLWZhYzdkM2YyNmQ1MSJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAUP_s7ymco96jdPrWx1c2okIoCB3frKOa87__I4_1XMR&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fossil.com%2Fen-us%2Fwatches%2Fsmartwatches%2F">​​Fossil</a> 、 <a data-i13n="cpos:14;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Michael Kors;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=9b64e7e9-b6f0-4d91-bb71-eef8d80fabea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Michael+Kors&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI5YjY0ZTdlOS1iNmYwLTRkOTEtYmI3MS1lZWY4ZDgwZmFiZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cubWljaGFlbGtvcnMuY29tL3dhdGNoZXMvc21hcnR3YXRjaGVzL18vTi0xbHExaThvIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI3ZjQzNGUxNi1hYWJlLTMxNGQtODhmMC1mYWM3ZDNmMjZkNTEifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAW1mPU5BdK0D4GfHnK-OELERLJpl7xgeNhrWI8klrS77&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.michaelkors.com%2Fwatches%2Fsmartwatches%2F_%2FN-1lq1i8o">Michael Kors</a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Skagen Denmark;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=de835634-eb1e-4390-bd94-e5983b38f543&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Skagen+Denmark&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiJkZTgzNTYzNC1lYjFlLTQzOTAtYmQ5NC1lNTk4M2IzOGY1NDMiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2thZ2VuLmNvbS9lbi11cy9zbWFydHdhdGNoZXMvc21hcnR3YXRjaGVzLyIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiN2Y0MzRlMTYtYWFiZS0zMTRkLTg4ZjAtZmFjN2QzZjI2ZDUxIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAclP_RzzZAQxGjhXKXymQLCukDvA9vfycrZ6Yr2Imrtu&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.skagen.com%2Fen-us%2Fsmartwatches%2Fsmartwatches%2F">Skagen</a>等品牌在从模拟手表中汲取灵感的时尚智能手表中找到了自己的定位。您还可以选择从<a data-i13n="cpos:16;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAe3LQONW6fvKqYduhC8jHy9-Qw3EyKc2lHlBSrwvW2MA&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FWithings-ScanWatch-Hybrid-Smartwatch-Oximeter%2Fdp%2FB08D6LNBPN%3F">Withings</a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:17;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Garmin;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=4c7f75f5-4803-438a-a506-12a0ccb4ede4&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Garmin&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI0YzdmNzVmNS00ODAzLTQzOGEtYTUwNi0xMmEwY2NiNGVkZTQiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZ2FybWluLmNvbS9lbi1VUy9jL3Nwb3J0cy1maXRuZXNzL2Zhc2hpb24taHlicmlkLXNtYXJ0d2F0Y2hlcy8_IiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI3ZjQzNGUxNi1hYWJlLTMxNGQtODhmMC1mYWM3ZDNmMjZkNTEifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAeNJTAOsCqs6v23yXaK7EXzpP8D5f_uxY0Tu1mWW0RXO&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.garmin.com%2Fen-US%2Fc%2Fsports-fitness%2Ffashion-hybrid-smartwatches%2F%3F">Garmin</a>等公司购买“混合”智能手表 - 这些设备看起来像标准手表，但包含一些有限的功能，例如活动跟踪和心率监测。如果您喜欢这种外观，它们仍然是不错的选择，但值得庆幸的是，苹果、三星、Fitbit 和其他公司生产的可穿戴设备在过去几年中变得越来越有吸引力。</p><p>最终，购买智能手表后唯一无法改变的是它的外壳设计。如果您不喜欢 Apple Watch 的方角，所有三星智能手表都有圆形表壳，看起来更像传统手表。大多数可穿戴设备都有多种颜色可供选择，您可以支付额外费用购买不锈钢等优质材料。一旦您决定了表壳，您的表带选择将是无穷无尽的——有数十种第一方和第三方表带可供大多数主要智能手表使用，并且适合较大和较小的手腕，让您可以随时改变自己的外观。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/best-smartwatches-153013118.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/best-smartwatches-153013118.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 7f434e16-aabe-314d-88f0-fac7d3f26d51</guid><dc:creator>瓦伦蒂娜·帕拉迪诺、切琳·洛</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jul 2023 19:00:16 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1689620417</ingested><modified> 2023-07-17T19:00:27+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[news]]></category><category><![CDATA[smartwatch]]></category><category><![CDATA[Google]]></category><category><![CDATA[Apple]]></category><category><![CDATA[thebuyersguide]]></category><category><![CDATA[Samsung]]></category><category><![CDATA[commerce]]></category><category><![CDATA[Fitbit]]></category><category><![CDATA[gear]]></category><category><![CDATA[ElectronicEquipment,Instruments&Components]]></category><category><![CDATA[ElectronicsAccessories]]></category><category><![CDATA[OfficeElectronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology&Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Information Technology]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Handheld & Connected Devices]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Valentina Palladino]]></category><media:content height="1204" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-12/45544550-7c97-11ed-be7f-b301bffa0c0d" width="1753"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1204" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-12/45544550-7c97-11ed-be7f-b301bffa0c0d" width="1753"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Cherlynn Low / Engadget]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[The Apple Watch Series 8 on a person's wrist, showing a paused workout tracking screen.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Apple Watch Series 8]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Threads users are already spending less time in the app]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> Meta 的 Threads 应用程序<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/one-week-in-threads-has-become-twitters-biggest-threat-140050889.html"><ins>在第一周</ins></a>就引起轰动，成为有史以来增长最快的应用程序后，又回到了现实。分析公司SimilarWeb的新数据表明，尽管该应用程序是有史以来<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/metas-threads-races-to-100-million-users-in-under-a-week-070740016.html"><ins>增长最快的</ins></a>应用程序，但其参与度已从最初的高点下降。</p><p> SameWeb 在一份<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.similarweb.com/blog/insights/social-media-news/threads-week/"><ins>新报告中写道，Threads 的日活跃用户从 7 月 7 日的 4900 万下降至 7 月 14 日的 2360 万。</ins></a>据报道，在美国，使用率最高，但同一时期的使用时间从每天 21 分钟下降到略多于 6 分钟。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>虽然SimilarWeb警告称，其数据仅基于Android对Threads的使用情况，但其调查结果与其他公司的结果一致。市场情报公司 Sensor Tower 报告称，参与度也出现了类似的下降，并在一份报告中写道，该应用“自推出以来，DAU（每日活跃用户）和用户参与度出现了两位数的下降。”</p><p>在某种程度上，这种下降是预料之中的。 Threads 推出之际，许多 Twitter 用户正在寻找替代方案，而它与 Instagram 的联系使用户可以非常轻松地注册并移植他们现有的社交图谱。与此同时，该应用程序缺少许多<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/all-the-questions-we-still-have-about-threads-153059430.html"><ins>基本功能</ins></a>，包括不易被品牌和影响者主导的非算法提要。</p><p> Instagram 的最高执行官 Adam Mosseri 在周五的 Threads 帖子中表示，公司现阶段并未特别关注参与度指标。他<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.threads.net/@mosseri/post/CusMDHkrG3w"><ins>写道</ins></a>：“我们现在的重点不是参与度，这真是太棒了，而是要克服我们在每个新产品上看到的最初的高峰和低谷，并构建新功能，提高性能，并提高排名。”</p><p> Meta 是否能够充分利用这些条件可能取决于它添加新功能以留住用户的速度有多快，以及它是否能够在<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/meta-blocks-eu-users-from-accessing-threads-through-a-vpn-135306350.html"><ins>欧盟</ins></a>境内推出。 Mosseri 表示，该公司还在处理垃圾邮件问题，他表示 Threads 将设置速率限制和其他保护措施。 “垃圾邮件攻击有所增加，因此我们必须在速率限制等方面采取更严格的措施，这将意味着更多无意中限制活跃用户（误报），”他<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.threads.net/@mosseri/post/Cuzo-AxtZ1o"><ins>写道</ins></a>。</p><p>虽然 Threads 的参与度下降对于 Twitter 来说似乎是个好消息，但该公司仍然有足够的理由<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/one-week-in-threads-has-become-twitters-biggest-threat-140050889.html"><ins>担心</ins></a>其最新的竞争对手。正如 SametimeWeb 的高级洞察经理 David Carr 所写，“一些迹象”表明，至少 Threads 的部分参与度是以 Twitter 的参与度为代价的。 “在 Threads 全面推出的前两天（星期四和星期五）中，twitter.com 的网络流量与前一周同一天相比下降了 5%，Android 应用程序使用量（按花费时间计算）下降了 4.3%， ”卡尔说。他还指出，自去年以来，“Twitter 用户保留率一直在下降”。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/threads-users-are-already-spending-less-time-in-the-app-182738755.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/threads-users-are-already-spending-less-time-in-the-app-182738755.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 1c41f0dc-ff99-4b31-b772-35a1ed6a5361</guid><dc:creator>卡丽莎·贝尔</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jul 2023 18:27:38 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1689618459</ingested><modified> 2023-07-17T18:27:44+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Software]]></category><category><![CDATA[Mobile Apps]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Karissa Bell]]></category><media:content height="2202" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/981ac190-24cd-11ee-9f9e-2f4437c45557" width="3303"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="2202" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/981ac190-24cd-11ee-9f9e-2f4437c45557" width="3303"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[STEFANI REYNOLDS via Getty Images]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[This photo illustration created  in Washington, DC, on July 6, 2023, shows the logo for Threads, an Instagram app, next to its page on the App Store. More than 10 million people have signed up to Threads, Meta's rival to Twitter, within the first few hours of its launch, the company's CEO Mark Zuckerberg said July 6. The app went live on Apple and Android app stores in 100 countries at 2300 GMT on July 5, 2023, and will run with no ads for now, but its release in Europe has been delayed over data privacy concerns. (Photo by Stefani Reynolds / AFP) (Photo by STEFANI REYNOLDS/AFP via Getty Images)]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[US-EU-TECH-THREADS-TWITTER]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[The best computer monitors for 2023]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>仅去年一年，电脑显示器就不断快速发展，出现了 OLED Flex、QD-OLED 和内置智能平台等新技术。除此之外，色彩准确性、图像质量、尺寸和分辨率等方面也有了重大改进。</p><p>这意味着您在选择最适合您的显示器时有很多选择，但这可能会让人不知所措，因为您必须筛选大量具有不同功能集的产品。购买电脑显示器的买家现在必须考虑 HDR、亮度、色彩精度、显示技术类型、输入延迟等因素。然后还有一些常见的考虑因素，例如尺寸、可调节性、输入等。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>为了帮助您实现这一切，我们研究了适合各种市场的最新型号，无论您是商业用户、内容创建者、多任务处理者还是竞技游戏爱好者。请阅读下面的购买指南，找出最适合您的电脑显示器，尤其是您的预算。 </p><iframe src="https://www.yahoo.com/monitor-specs-nonsense-upscaled-050905179.html?format=embed&amp;region=US&amp;lang=en-US&amp;site=engadget&amp;player_autoplay=false&amp;recommendations=false" allowfullscreen="true" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" data-yom-embed-source="{media_id_1:aa3a0745-3d1e-3f37-9b01-1563484163f5}" data-yahoo-uuid="aa3a0745-3d1e-3f37-9b01-1563484163f5"></iframe><h2>基础</h2><h3>面板型</h3><p>最便宜的显示器仍然是 TN（扭曲向列），仅限游戏或办公室使用。 VA（垂直排列）显示器也相对便宜，同时提供良好的亮度和高对比度。然而，内容创作者会发现 IPS（面内切换）LCD 显示器可提供更好的色彩精度、图像质量和视角。</p><p>如果最大亮度很重要，那么量子点 LCD 显示器是最佳选择——这些显示器通常出现在较大的显示器中。 OLED 显示器现已上市，可提供最佳的黑色和色彩再现，但它们缺乏 LED 或量子点显示器的亮度。另外，它们的成本很高。三星的最新类型 OLED 显示器名为 QD-OLED，于 2022 年刚刚推出。最显着的优点是它可以变得更亮，CES 2022 上展示的显示器峰值亮度高达 1,000 尼特。</p><p> MiniLED现已广泛应用于高端显示器。它们类似于量子点技术，但顾名思义，它使用直径仅为 0.2 毫米的较小 LED 二极管。因此，制造商可以封装多达三倍的 LED 和更多的局部调光区域，从而提供更深的黑色和更好的对比度。</p><h3>屏幕尺寸、分辨率和显示格式</h3><p>在当今时代，屏幕尺寸占据主导地位。 24 英寸显示器曾经或多或少是标准显示器（并且仍然可用于基本计算），而 27 英寸、32 英寸、34 英寸甚至 42 英寸显示器如今已在娱乐、内容创建甚至游戏中变得流行。</p><p>过去几乎所有显示器都是 16:9 的，但现在可以找到 16:10 和其他更奇特的显示器形状。在游戏和娱乐方面，我们还看到宽高比为 21:9 的曲面超宽显示器。不过，如果您决定购买超宽显示器，请记住，30 英寸 21:9 型号的高度与 24 英寸显示器相同，因此您最终可能会得到比您预期更小的显示器。 As a rule of thumb, add 25 percent to the size of a 21:9 monitor to get the vertical height you&#39;d expect from a model with a 16:9 aspect ratio.</p><p> A 4K monitor is nearly a must for content creators, and some folks are even going for 5K or all the way up to 8K. Keep in mind, though, that you&#39;ll need a pretty powerful computer to drive all those pixels. And 4K resolution should be paired with a screen size of 27 inches and up, or you won&#39;t notice much difference between 1440p. At the same time, I wouldn&#39;t get a model larger than 27 inches unless it&#39;s 4K, as you&#39;ll start to see pixelation if you&#39;re working up close to the display.</p><p> One new category to consider is <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2019-05-27-asus-240hz-portable-monitor-for-gamers-hands-on.html">portable monitors</a> designed to be carried and used with laptops. Those typically come in 1080p resolutions and sizes from 13-15 inches. They usually have a lightweight kickstand-type support that folds up to keep things compact. </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-07/e19ecb10-fd3f-11ec-a77d-fca8b8a4ea1f" alt="Samsung Smart Monitor M5" data-uuid="49c68616-2f8d-3632-b151-bb29fe67d558"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">三星</div></figure><h3>HDR</h3><p> HDR is the buzzy monitor feature to have these days, as it adds vibrancy to entertainment and gaming – but be careful before jumping in. Some monitors that claim HDR on the marketing materials don&#39;t even conform to a base standard. To be sure that a display at least meets minimum HDR specs, you&#39;ll want to choose one with a DisplayHDR rating with each tier representing maximum brightness in nits.</p><p> However, the lowest DisplayHDR 400 and 500 tiers may disappoint you with a lack of brightness, washed out blacks and mediocre color reproduction. If you can afford it, the best monitor to choose is a model with DisplayHDR 600, 1000 or True Black 400, True Black 500 and True Black 600. The True Black settings are designed primarily for OLED models, with maximum black levels at .0005 nits.</p><p> Where televisions typically offer HDR10 and Dolby Vision or HDR10+, most PC monitors only support the HDR10 standard, other than a few (very expensive) models. That doesn&#39;t matter much for content creation or gaming, but HDR streaming on Netflix, Amazon Prime Video and other services won&#39;t look quite as punchy. In addition, most models supporting HDR600 (and up) are gaming monitors, rather than content creation monitors – with a few exceptions.</p><h3> Refresh rate</h3><p> Refresh rate is a key feature, particularly on gaming monitors. A bare minimum nowadays is 60Hz, and 80Hz and higher refresh rates are much easier on the eyes. However, most 4K displays top out at 60Hz with some rare exceptions and the HDMI 2.0 spec only supports 4K at 60Hz, so you&#39;d need at least DisplayPort 1.4 (4K at 120Hz) or HDMI 2.1. The latter is now available on a number of monitors, particularly gaming displays. However, it&#39;s only supported on the latest NVIDIA RTX 3000- and 4000-series, AMD RX 6000-series GPUs.</p><h3> Inputs</h3><p> There are essentially three types of modern display inputs: Thunderbolt, DisplayPort and HDMI. Most monitors built for PCs come with the latter two, while a select few (typically built for Macs) will use Thunderbolt. To add to the confusion, USB-C ports may be Thunderbolt 3 and by extension, DisplayPort compatible, so you may need a USB-C to Thunderbolt or DisplayPort cable adapter depending on your display.</p><h3> Color bit depth</h3><p> Serious content creators should consider a more costly 10-bit monitor that can display billions of colors. If budget is an issue, you can go for an 8-bit panel that can fake billions of colors via dithering (often spec&#39;d as “8-bit + FRC”). For entertainment or business purposes, a regular 8-bit monitor that can display millions of colors will be fine.</p><h3> Color gamut</h3><p> The other aspect of color is the gamut. That expresses the range of colors that can be reproduced and not just the number of colors. Most good monitors these days can cover the sRGB and Rec.709 gamuts (designed for photos and video respectively). For more demanding work, though, you&#39;ll want one that can reproduce more demanding modern gamuts like AdobeRGB, DCI-P3 and Rec.2020 gamuts, which encompass a wider range of colors. The latter two are often used for film projection and HDR, respectively.</p><h3> Console gaming</h3><p> Both the Xbox Series X and Sony&#39;s PS5 can handle 4K 120Hz HDR gaming, so if you&#39;re into resolution over pure speed, you&#39;ll want a monitor that can keep up. 4K resolution, HDR and at least 120Hz is the minimum starting point, but fortunately there are 27-inch displays with those specs starting at well under $1,000.</p><h3> Pricing and parts shortages</h3><p> Though the pandemic has eased, monitor supply is still a bit tighter than pre-pandemic levels due to supply and demand issues. To that end, you may have trouble finding monitors at Amazon, B&amp;H or elsewhere for the suggested retail price. For our guide below, we&#39;re basing our picks on the MSRP, as long as the street price doesn&#39;t exceed that by more than $25.</p><h2> Best monitors under $200</h2><h3> Samsung T35F </h3><p><core-commerce id="36e56d959fe8486da79302fce5bca6ca" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> The best budget monitor with a balance of size, refresh rate and color accuracy is <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9ncC9wcm9kdWN0L0IwOEZGM0pRMjg_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tZ2ktMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjAwN2Y5NmU3LTBlYzktM2E3OS1hNmFlLWQ1MjcxNjQzY2RiZCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAVcVzY4R9Rbo06z-D5LiuAwJXPA7apE1vO6D-sfqg9lc&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB08FF3JQ28">Samsung&#39;s 27-inch 1080p T35F</a> . It&#39;s good for business or light gaming and content work, thanks to the IPS panel and 75Hz refresh rate. Plus, it&#39;s fairly attractive and modern looking. There are some things you don&#39;t get at that price, of course – it can only tilt and has an HDMI 1.4 connection.</p><h3> LG 24GL600F </h3><p><core-commerce id="aa2eacf03af84922a871f9dba4e1afc4" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> If you&#39;re fine with a smaller display and are more into gaming, another solid option is <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAcumfQY74RiUebbsns5tjnEOsaBFnzc8_xAya0A0mlBr&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB07NHSJ1RF%2F">LG&#39;s 24-inch 24GL600F</a> . It offers a high refresh rate of 144Hz with AMD FreeSync support, a 1ms response time and low input lag. You also get HDMI and DisplayPort inputs, but like the T35F, there&#39;s no height adjustment.</p><h2> Best monitors under $400</h2><h3> HP U28 4K HDR Monitor </h3><p><core-commerce id="d3af211da7a5433481592c99b76e2892" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> The <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAdN6Tai2dYq8lHcJXWASx_RQlSn1Yxf5jrkpAYimWLdp&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB08HVV2T3K%2F">28-inch HP U28 4K HDR monitor</a> is a great all around choice, especially for content creators. The 60Hz IPS panel and factory calibration delivers excellent color accuracy and it&#39;s a nice size for creative or business work. It comes with DisplayPort, HDMI and three USB 3.0 ports, along with a USB-C port with 65W of charging for a laptop or tablet. And it&#39;s easy to set just right, thanks to height, swivel and pivot adjustment.</p><h3> Gigabyte G27QC </h3><p><core-commerce id="bd0f6d7a65da4743bcd9183d5b2088b2" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> If gaming is more your thing, the <a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;e